OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,6,Fwith variable amounts of cloud. Some
OL,7,Fsunny intervals, more especially
OL,8,Facross the southwest. Warm in any
OL,9,Fsunshine in the southwest, otherwise
OL,10,Fcooler than Tuesday in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then it will
OL,14,Fmainly dry with clear periods, the odd
OL,15,Fshower possible in the southwest later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,18,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Becoming
OL,19,Fvery warm, locally hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
